text: And the Winner Is (Originally released as Female Vocalist of the Year and The Winner Is... Selena & Los Dinos) is the third LP record release from Mexican- American Tejano pop band Selena y Los Dinos. == Track listing == == Re-release == This album was re-released entitled Classic Series, Vol. 3 in 2007.
